# Wayfare Frontend

## Config

- API base: `process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` in `web/lib/api.ts` — must be set at Vercel build time
- Local dev: copy `web/.env.example` → `web/.env.local`

## City Toggle

- Active city lives in Zustand (`web/lib/store.ts` → `city` / `setCity`)
- `TopBar` uses buttons + `router.replace`, not URL-only local state
- `CitySync` keeps URL `?city=` and store aligned
- Search page reads city from store; patch handlers call `setCity` when filters include city

## Components

- `"use client"` only where needed (hooks, map, store, SSE)
- Map: MapLibre + OSM tiles in `ResultsMap.tsx`; refit on new search via `fitKey`
- Concierge: SSE via `web/lib/stream.ts`; dock in `ConciergeDock.tsx`

## UI

- Palette: brand blue + amber accent; fonts Bricolage Grotesque + Inter (see `layout.tsx`)
- Keep booking-style UX; AI features show understood filter chips and agent steps

## Docker

- Production image runs `next start`; rebuild image after frontend changes when using `docker compose --profile web`
